node.title: Whangārei mayor hopes vaccine pass will encourage unvaccinated to rethink
node.description: The red traffic light is more restrictive than level 2 but is in place in Northland for a good reason - low vaccination rates, Whangārei Mayor Sheryl Mai says. Audio

node.title: After months of hints, Matthew McConaughey rules out bid to be next celebrity politician
node.description: After publicly weighing up whether to run for office in America's second-largest state, Matthew McConaughey says he will instead focus on supporting businesses and foundations that create pathways for others to succeed.

node.title: Police search old mining site for bodies of allegedly murdered campers Russell Hill and Carol Clay
node.description: The head of the Victoria Police Missing Persons Squad has arrived at a remote area of bushland to help search for the remains of the missing campers.
